text: Hybolasius parvus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Broun in 1880. It is known from New Zealand. It contains the varietas Hybolasius parvus var. pusillus.BioLib.cz - Hybolasius parvus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1880
